Rating: 4
DeLLICCious! Perfectly fluffy, moist (more so than normal) and almost custardy interior. They raise very high and survive freezing beautifully. The recipe was quick to put together and is even entirely manageable completely by hand. HOWEVER, be SURE to replace the amount of pumpkin pie spice with 1 1/2 tsp. cinnamon, 3/4 tsp. ground ginger, 3/8 tsp. ground cloves, and 1/4-1/2 t. freshly grated nutmeg. I found this ratio and amount to be practically perfect. Enjoy!

